From cc45eb2dc40a5fcd0c2d87320acd85fd4cf000e2 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Tue, 14 Jul 2026 05:13:03 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] Make Gecko navigation lifecycle native
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

The fox now journals every turn,
No sampled tales or status urn.
Each tab keeps sequence, truth, and track—
Then native keys go forward, reload, and back.
